message.content: Adapt this product to be a airbnb concierge. It will use subagents to customize the experiences to the next level. - Make the nodes airbnb logos. All of them must have airbnb logos and branding. subagents will have their task icon + airbnbs - "Hardcode" 5 main subagents. Each subagent depth is 1, hardcode that too, but keep the top depth slider for aethetic (each one with respective logos related to their tasks): Yelp review reader (pencil), Airbnb's proprietary user data for customization (User icons), Google Maps explorer scraping of nearby interesting places (pin), Reddit agent(message icon), Luma (ticket icons) - Add a fake tokens counter. It should go from 0 to 20M and it should start only whe execution starts. It should feel real and should be minimalistic placed
